ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 207, Manitoba
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 207 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of MANITOBA, with respect to the spring floods that occurred from March 21, 2017 until July 10, 2017, which affected many communities.
